data.description: Enjoy the Westminster lifestyle in this fabulous 3 bedroom, 2 bath home. Built in 2011 with a well-planned open floorplan, and vaulted ceiling. The large Master offers an ensuite and a walk in closet with ample space ! This move in ready home, {USDA Eligible!} Is conveniently located,within minutes to town, Clemson is a 20 minute drive, and Anderson is only 40 minutes away! The back patio is designed for entertaining! Schedule your appointment to view this pristine property today !
